fish: W-where am I?
narrator: Welcome to Fish Out of Water!
narrator: To move your character, use WASD. To move the camera, use the keyboard's arrow keys. The camera controls are inverted.
narrator: Red platforms will start to fall once you touch them. You can click space bar twice to double jump.
narrator: Your goal is to collect at least 12 coins and make it to the purple flag without falling to buy a bigger (and less dangerous) fish tank for yourself.